{"tid":1147832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生仔嘅意義係乜","createTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T05:02:31.000Z","uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c04da22a44a6f7a40ccf429ec52d6cea129d03a","tid":1147832,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"煩呢樣煩嗰樣 唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12e372c185656e80e929928341e6e09fa0225a9","tid":1147832,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267ee3e8136ec3471ee4ac12d40d2826723817cb","tid":1147832,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月10日 星期五 夜晚8:00-9:30 (部分團體通宵留守至星期六)<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"baae5adf421596b801ed7b904a4e54fef838d231","tid":1147832,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd70e127d93fdd6b133eb7db3e736b1195bd48d","tid":1147832,"uid":102872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"浪費你既金錢，時間，感情，人生"},{"pid":"c145b7d177a8a412a929d6884374d5b434fef27a","tid":1147832,"uid":54488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"真係咪撚生<br />\n香港嘅財富集中晒喺少數靠物業炒賣致富嘅有錢人手上<br />\n生個仔出嚟只會成為負責供養依班有錢人嘅奴隸<br />\n個社會已經搞到我哋咁慘，我哋冇義務生仔為依個社會提供勞動力 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038ed86430780ec15679e6d9c5da96495c32abac","tid":1147832,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}